{
  "stem": "4289.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The television came from Gdansk, and they took a picture of our meeting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And television came from Israel too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because I said they have the same right to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There's not only Polish television.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they took pictures.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were in the news.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And friends saw me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my aunt Ester saw me in Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And since then on, I stayed in Poland for a while.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we started to go back to our roots to find out what can we find out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was sure that-- that easy I'll have his birth certificate and my birth certificate is there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It has to be Adam's.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "When we went to the Bureau in the City Hall, and I told them the name, they said, there is no such person.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because I wrote ahead of time that I'm coming to Poland if Adam is there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Sosnowiec, In our own city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I heard that his birth certificate isn't there, I got hysterical.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I cried so hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had to take me out of the room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, how is it possible?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they went to the archives and brought it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And said, because your birth certificate was made in 1949.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not the original from 1939.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's why he doesn't have.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, that's impossible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Look for my sister birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was born probably seven years earlier, whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they say, all those papers are destroyed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We did find the birth certificate of another Genia Paluch in 1937.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that was my uncle in Israel for his daughter that he lost also in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because now he has a second family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He started all over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe-- well, maybe for Genia, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For-- but for sure not for the two of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
